.TH LOA-FIND-COMPOSER 1 "2026-03-23" "Library Of Alexandria" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
find composer \- Search sheet music by composer substring
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> find composer
.SH DESCRIPTION
Prompts for a composer query and shows matching \fBSheetMusic\fR entries.
.br
Matching is case-insensitive and works with partial names.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
alexandria> find composer
.br
Composer search: bach
.SH SEE ALSO
loa(1), loa-find-author(1), loa-list-sheet(1), loa-list-instrument(1)
